1 Section 1. Chapter 701A of NRS is hereby amended by
2 adding thereto the provisions set forth as sections 2 and 3 of this act.
3 Sec. 2. “Agrivoltaics” means a system in which agricultural
4 activities, including, without limitation, crop production, livestock
5 production or beekeeping, occur underneath or between solar
6 panels.
7 Sec. 3. “Ecovoltaics” means a system in which conservation
8 activities, including, without limitation, native species
9 conservation, rangeland enhancement, soil improvement,
10 brownfield remediation or the fostering of pollinator habitats,
11 occur underneath or between solar panels.
